1
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:04,200
Ja

2
00:00:04,600 --> 00:00:06,000
Ne, nema veze.

3
00:00:06,200 --> 00:00:07,100
Šta?

4
00:00:07,700 --> 00:00:09,200
Samo da kažem ko sam?

5
00:00:10,200 --> 00:00:11,200
U redu, moje ime je Ricard Mejhju

6
00:00:12,200 --> 00:00:13,100
I...

7
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:15,200
Ja sam u obezbedenju

8
00:00:15,250 --> 00:00:17,250
- Džesika, 'ajde... dodi i rci zdravo.
- O, Ricarde

9
00:00:18,100 --> 00:00:19,000
Zdravo.

10
00:00:19,200 --> 00:00:21,165
London, da, veoma lijep

11
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:23,251
Živim ovdje
vec par godina

12
00:00:23,700 --> 00:00:25,200
i više se ne gubim u podzemnoj.

13
00:00:27,200 --> 00:00:29,200
Da vidimo, volim kari.

14
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:30,435
Sakupljam one sicušne...

15
00:00:30,436 --> 00:00:33,578
- ... plasticne okruglaste stvarcice.
- Ricarde, molim te.

16
00:00:33,613 --> 00:00:34,800
Ne volim.

17
00:00:34,941 --> 00:00:36,878
Visine... Ne volim visine.

18
00:00:36,978 --> 00:00:37,878
Mrzim visine.

19
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:40,713
Ne znam, uobicajene stvari,
pretpostavljam.

20
00:00:41,200 --> 00:00:42,100
Pacove.

21
00:00:42,300 --> 00:00:43,200
Krv.

22
00:00:43,381 --> 00:00:44,293
I tako to.

23
00:00:45,200 --> 00:00:46,200
Opisati sebe

24
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:47,900
Normalan

25
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:50,200
Dosadan

26
00:00:51,675 --> 00:00:53,300
Dobro se ismijati.

27
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:56,200
Je li to u redu?

28
00:01:40,583 --> 00:01:43,583
Prva epizoda:
DOOR (V R A T A)

29
00:02:31,783 --> 00:02:35,783
Sad, eto jednog pacova koji
više nece pricati price.

30
00:02:36,483 --> 00:02:38,343
Pacov. Price.

31
00:02:54,483 --> 00:02:55,383
<i>Zdravo, Ricarde?</i>

32
00:02:55,487 --> 00:02:56,775
<i>Izvršni direktor
bi da zna kada</i>

33
00:02:56,823 --> 00:02:57,776
<i>ce imati izvještaj</i>

34
00:02:57,883 --> 00:02:59,255
Možeš li mi dati 5 minuta, Silvija?

35
00:02:59,303 --> 00:03:00,703
Skoro je gotov

36
00:03:01,607 --> 00:03:03,623
<i>Hvala, Dik. Sici cu po njega.</i>

37
00:03:33,583 --> 00:03:34,483
Mejhju

38
00:03:34,983 --> 00:03:36,583
<i>Ricarde? Džesika je.</i>

39
00:03:36,955 --> 00:03:37,825
Džes...

40
00:03:37,826 --> 00:03:39,322
Džesika, Ricarde, ne Džes.

41
00:03:40,403 --> 00:03:41,584
<i>Potvrdio si našu rezervaciju
za veceras, zar ne?</i>

42
00:03:42,770 --> 00:03:44,261
Nisi zaboravio, zar ne?"

43
00:03:44,607 --> 00:03:46,583
Zaboravio? Ne, nisam zaboravio.

44
00:03:47,183 --> 00:03:48,483
Ma Maison at 7:30.

45
00:03:50,030 --> 00:03:51,097
Da se nadjemo tamo?

46
00:03:51,637 --> 00:03:52,583
Nakon onog što se desilo posljednji put?

47
00:03:52,709 --> 00:03:54,737
Ricarde, ti se možeš izgubiti
u vlastitiom dvorištu.

48
00:03:56,083 --> 00:03:58,194
Naci cemo se kod tebe i
možemo odšetati do tamo.

49
00:03:58,353 --> 00:03:59,464
Važi, Džes... Izvini! Džesika.

50
00:03:59,583 --> 00:04:00,583
Dobro.

51
00:04:30,413 --> 00:04:31,343
Ricard Mejhju

52
00:04:33,061 --> 00:04:34,222
<i>Zdravo, Dik...</i>

53
00:04:34,463 --> 00:04:35,434
<i>To sam ja, Gari</i>

54
00:04:37,083 --> 00:04:37,983
Geri...

55
00:04:38,534 --> 00:04:39,766
Jesmo li još uvijek za ono pice?

56
00:04:39,927 --> 00:04:42,835
Skidaj se s prokletog telefona,
Gari. Naravno da jesmo.

57
00:04:45,783 --> 00:04:48,107
Onda, gospodine Vandemar.
Ona usporava

58
00:04:49,447 --> 00:04:50,483
Usporava, gospodine Krup.

59
00:04:50,933 --> 00:04:52,583
Mora da gubi mnogo krvi
gospodine V

60
00:04:53,101 --> 00:04:56,373
Divne krvi, gospodine
K. Divne, vlažne krvi,

61
00:04:57,483 --> 00:04:58,983
Nece još zadugo.

62
00:05:02,083 --> 00:05:02,983
Dik!

63
00:05:03,783 --> 00:05:05,774
Dik, prošlo je 7.

64
00:05:05,897 --> 00:05:06,899
Koliko?

65
00:05:08,583 --> 00:05:09,683
Ubice me.

66
00:05:10,583 --> 00:05:13,183
Nacicemo se kasnije Gari. Vidimo se.

67
00:05:15,183 --> 00:05:16,367
Znaci, naše se pice otkazuje?

68
00:05:24,983 --> 00:05:26,183
Ricarde... šta to radiš?

69
00:05:27,072 --> 00:05:27,882
Ništa, Džesika.

70
00:05:27,883 --> 00:05:28,783
Dobro. Sad...

71
00:05:29,380 --> 00:05:31,277
Gospodin Stokton nije
samo moj šef, Ricarde,

72
00:05:31,752 --> 00:05:33,881
On je takoder i osoba u
korporaciji sa svim pravima.

73
00:05:34,884 --> 00:05:36,683
Stoga je presudno da veceras
ostaviš dobar utisak.

74
00:05:38,533 --> 00:05:39,331
Jedva cekam.

75
00:05:39,332 --> 00:05:39,913
Šta si rekao?

76
00:05:39,914 --> 00:05:40,814
Jedva cekam!

77
00:05:41,783 --> 00:05:43,083
Možeš li mi dati nešto sice, druže?

78
00:05:43,283 --> 00:05:45,183
Ricarde, nemamo vremena.

79
00:05:45,283 --> 00:05:47,483
Gospodin Stokton pomalo
cjepidlaci oko tacnosti.

80
00:05:48,583 --> 00:05:50,545
O, Ricarde, Ja te doista volim.
Znaš to, zar ne?

81
00:05:51,254 --> 00:05:54,159
Jedini razlog zbog kog te pritišcem je
stoga što želim da pružisš ono najbolje.

82
00:06:09,583 --> 00:06:12,483
Nek pakao blagoslovi moja malu crnu
dušu, gospodine Vandemar,

83
00:06:13,895 --> 00:06:15,091
vidite li ono što i ja,

84
00:06:16,100 --> 00:06:18,260
Spazih, svojim okom malim,

85
00:06:18,636 --> 00:06:20,403
nešto što ce biti-

86
00:06:20,503 --> 00:06:23,307
Mrtvo za trenutak, gospodine Krup.

87
00:06:30,675 --> 00:06:31,739
Baksuz!

88
00:06:36,411 --> 00:06:38,283
...i veoma je važno da se
smiješ njegovim šalama.

89
00:06:38,716 --> 00:06:40,248
Ako su u bilo kakvoj neudoumici
da li da se nasmiješ ili ne...

90
00:06:40,403 --> 00:06:41,979
- ... samo prati moj mig.
- Džesika.

91
00:06:42,883 --> 00:06:43,883
- Džesika!
- Molim?

92
00:06:44,403 --> 00:06:45,403
Gledaj.

93
00:06:45,883 --> 00:06:47,486
Ako im pridaješ imalo pažnje,
Ricarde, neceš ih se moci otarasiti.

94
00:06:48,283 --> 00:06:49,283
Oni svi imaju domove, doista.

95
00:06:49,583 --> 00:06:51,391
Sad. Rekla sam gospodinu
Stoktonu da cemo...

96
00:06:52,599 --> 00:06:53,893
Ricarde? Šta to radiš?

97
00:06:54,083 --> 00:06:56,006
Ona je povrijedena. Krvari.

98
00:06:56,356 --> 00:06:57,983
Ricarde. Zakasnicemo.

99
00:06:58,183 --> 00:06:59,083
Ona je povrijedena!

100
00:06:59,410 --> 00:07:00,380
Ricarde.

101
00:07:00,722 --> 00:07:01,697
Odvedi me negdje na sigurno.

102
00:07:01,897 --> 00:07:02,883
Pronaci ce me.

103
00:07:03,783 --> 00:07:04,783
Pomozi mi.

104
00:07:05,386 --> 00:07:07,408
Vidi. Pozovi hitnu pomoc,

105
00:07:07,513 --> 00:07:08,424
ali nemoj dati svoje ime.

106
00:07:09,583 --> 00:07:11,502
Ne, molim vas.

107
00:07:12,589 --> 00:07:13,489
Ne bolnicu.

108
00:07:14,498 --> 00:07:15,959
Možda ceš morati dati
izjavu ili nešto takvo,

109
00:07:16,135 --> 00:07:17,883
a ja necu da mi ovo vece
upropasti jedna...

110
00:07:18,340 --> 00:07:20,404
Ricarde Olivere Mejhju,
spusti tu mladu osobu

111
00:07:20,583 --> 00:07:21,907
i dolazi ovamo istog trena.

112
00:07:22,278 --> 00:07:24,283
Ili su ove zaruke na svom kraju,
kao što je od sad.

113
00:07:25,583 --> 00:07:26,583
Upozoravam te.

114
00:07:27,883 --> 00:07:28,783
Sranje!

115
00:07:38,283 --> 00:07:39,183
Kljucevi!

116
00:07:39,961 --> 00:07:41,183
Gdje su mi kljucevi?

117
00:07:51,583 --> 00:07:52,933
Nije ih mogla ni zatvoriti kako treba.

118
00:08:02,583 --> 00:08:06,812
Slušaj...pozvacu ljekara.

119
00:08:08,483 --> 00:08:09,803
Ne, ne...

120
00:08:10,458 --> 00:08:13,283
Molim te, nemoj.

121
00:08:13,983 --> 00:08:16,583
Nije tako loše kao što izgleda.

122
00:08:17,508 --> 00:08:19,483
Samo mi je potreban san, Bicu dobro.

123
00:08:21,184 --> 00:08:22,263
Bez ljekara.

124
00:08:25,083 --> 00:08:26,083
Ali tvoja ruka...

125
00:09:17,428 --> 00:09:18,854
Loši snovi?

126
00:09:19,806 --> 00:09:22,145
Da...tako nekako.

127
00:09:23,679 --> 00:09:24,983
Onda, ustala si se.

128
00:09:26,285 --> 00:09:27,520
Cija je ovo baronija?

129
00:09:28,121 --> 00:09:29,021
Ciji feud?

130
00:09:29,683 --> 00:09:30,502
Izvini?

131
00:09:30,503 --> 00:09:31,403
Gdje sam to ja?

132
00:09:31,732 --> 00:09:35,724
Stan 3. Njutn Mansioni...
Little Comden ulica...

133
00:09:36,583 --> 00:09:37,932
Ja sam u gornjem Londonu?

134
00:09:38,613 --> 00:09:39,903
Da...ti si u Londonu.

135
00:09:41,614 --> 00:09:44,403
Sinoc sam te pronašao
na ulici, sjecaš se?

136
00:09:45,184 --> 00:09:47,083
Bilo je... Bilo je mnogo krvi.

137
00:09:47,290 --> 00:09:48,218
Ne brini.

138
00:09:48,425 --> 00:09:50,456
Vecina krvi je pripadala
nekom drugom.

139
00:10:05,583 --> 00:10:06,730
Kako se zoveš?

140
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:12,368
Ricard... Ricard Mejhju...

141
00:10:13,574 --> 00:10:14,499
Dik.

142
00:10:14,509 --> 00:10:16,133
Ricardricardmejhjudik...

143
00:10:18,312 --> 00:10:20,683
O, Gospode! To mora da je Džes..

144
00:10:23,714 --> 00:10:24,614
Ubice me.

145
00:10:25,177 --> 00:10:26,743
U redu...ti sacekaj ovdje.

146
00:10:32,553 --> 00:10:34,557
Dobro vam jutro, dobri gospodine,

147
00:10:34,892 --> 00:10:36,523
na ovaj lijep i predivan dan.

148
00:10:37,094 --> 00:10:37,994
Ah. Zdravo.

149
00:10:38,232 --> 00:10:41,169
Mi provodimo licno istraživanje

150
00:10:41,639 --> 00:10:45,099
složene prirode, kakvo vec jeste,
od vrata do vrata.

151
00:10:45,591 --> 00:10:47,572
Da li bi vam smetalo, ako bi ušli?

152
00:10:49,783 --> 00:10:51,483
Zapravo, i nije...

153
00:10:51,788 --> 00:10:53,789
Sad baš i nije podesno

154
00:10:55,837 --> 00:10:57,205
Da li ste radite za policiju?

155
00:10:57,572 --> 00:11:00,804
Teško nama, ne možemo ustvrditi
takvo blaženstvo.

156
00:11:01,441 --> 00:11:03,039
Karijera od reda i zakona,

157
00:11:03,345 --> 00:11:07,641
premda nesumnjivo primamljiva,
nije bila zapisana u kartama,

158
00:11:07,742 --> 00:11:10,651
koje je Gospa Fortuna,
dodjelila mom bratu i meni.

159
00:11:11,524 --> 00:11:13,056
Ne, mi smo prosto obicni gradani.

160
00:11:13,784 --> 00:11:17,098
Dozvolite mi da se predstavimo.

161
00:11:17,641 --> 00:11:18,541
Ja sam gospodin Krup,

162
00:11:19,278 --> 00:11:21,279
a ovaj je gospodin, moj
brat, gospodin Vandemar.

163
00:11:21,883 --> 00:11:22,850
Vaš brat?

164
00:11:23,195 --> 00:11:24,995
Zar ne bi trebali imati isto prezime?

165
00:11:25,386 --> 00:11:27,189
kakav mozak, gospodine Vandemar.

166
00:11:27,483 --> 00:11:29,174
Oštrouman i britak
nije ni pola opisa.

167
00:11:29,514 --> 00:11:33,973
Neki od nas su tako britki...
mogli bi se lako posjeci.

168
00:11:34,552 --> 00:11:35,578
Šta želite?

169
00:11:36,254 --> 00:11:38,419
Tražimo našu
malu sestru...Dorin.

170
00:11:39,057 --> 00:11:41,924
Jogunasto dijete,
svojevoljnu i tvrdoglavu,

171
00:11:42,191 --> 00:11:44,719
koja, cak i dok razgovaramo,
istražuje ulice Londona...

172
00:11:45,027 --> 00:11:47,391
...nevoljena i nepažena.

173
00:11:48,730 --> 00:11:52,495
Gotovo da je slomila srce našoj
jadnoj, dragoj majci udovici.

174
00:11:53,132 --> 00:11:55,397
Pobjegla.

175
00:11:57,268 --> 00:12:01,769
Ona je pomalo... cudna.

176
00:12:03,272 --> 00:12:05,197
Ne... nisam je vidio.

177
00:12:05,483 --> 00:12:06,602
Žao mi je.

178
00:12:09,844 --> 00:12:11,535
Šta to misliš da radiš?

179
00:12:12,213 --> 00:12:14,510
Prestani! Odlazite.

180
00:12:14,815 --> 00:12:16,110
Ako vas dvoje ne izadete
telefoniracu policiji.

181
00:12:16,617 --> 00:12:19,611
Mislio sam da bi mi trebao
toalet... Ali nije. Izvinite.

182
00:12:20,660 --> 00:12:22,684
Reci cete nam, ako je vidite.

183
00:12:23,591 --> 00:12:24,720
Zbogom!

184
00:12:27,039 --> 00:12:29,603
Pljunuti.

185
00:12:31,477 --> 00:12:32,553
Jesi li mu povjerovao?

186
00:12:32,716 --> 00:12:35,252
Jesam davola. Mogao sam je namirisati. "

187
00:12:36,583 --> 00:12:37,392
Halo?

188
00:12:37,393 --> 00:12:39,081
- Ovdje Džesika.
- Džesika

189
00:12:39,373 --> 00:12:40,583
<i>Sinoc si me duboko
osramotio, Ricarde.</i>

190
00:12:40,733 --> 00:12:41,383
Halo? Džes?

191
00:12:41,384 --> 00:12:44,184
Što se neme tice
naša je vjeridba okoncana.

192
00:12:44,403 --> 00:12:48,113
- Džes, ovdje sam. - nemam
namjeru vracati prsten,

193
00:12:48,414 --> 00:12:49,363
niti stvarno da te
ikada više vidim.

194
00:12:49,423 --> 00:12:52,873
- Vjerujem da ce te ti i tvoja nova dragana
gorjeti u paklu. - Džesika!

195
00:12:53,073 --> 00:12:54,073
<i>Zbogom</i>

196
00:12:54,973 --> 00:12:56,441
- Loše vijesti?
- Da!

197
00:12:57,773 --> 00:12:58,673
Veoma loše.

198
00:13:01,390 --> 00:13:02,720
Ja jesam na fotografiji.

199
00:13:03,604 --> 00:13:06,779
I ti si...Dorin?

200
00:13:06,917 --> 00:13:09,812
Ja sam Dor (Door-vrata),
Ricardricard-mejhjudik

201
00:13:10,229 --> 00:13:11,161
Mlijeko i šecer?

202
00:13:11,699 --> 00:13:14,659
Ricard...samo Ricard.

203
00:13:15,167 --> 00:13:16,469
Bez šecera.

204
00:13:18,905 --> 00:13:21,567
Vidi, ako ovo nije
previše licno pitanje...

205
00:13:22,192 --> 00:13:23,108
šta ti se dogodilo?

206
00:13:23,341 --> 00:13:24,512
Ne želiš da znaš.

207
00:13:24,622 --> 00:13:26,216
O, dobro. Izvini.

208
00:13:26,623 --> 00:13:30,421
Ricarde, iskreno
ne želiš da znaš.

209
00:13:31,083 --> 00:13:32,217
To ti ne bi donijelo ništa dobra.

210
00:13:32,386 --> 00:13:34,760
Vec si uradio više no si trebao.

211
00:13:35,337 --> 00:13:39,201
Pa. Mislim. Nisam te mogao
samo tako ostaviti.

212
00:13:39,605 --> 00:13:42,503
Mogao si...I nisi.

213
00:13:50,077 --> 00:13:51,540
Pa, gdje si bila? Upravo?

214
00:13:51,882 --> 00:13:52,950
Bila sam ovdje.

215
00:13:53,748 --> 00:13:56,043
Slušaj, ova su dvojica još u blizini.

216
00:13:56,321 --> 00:13:59,633
Moramo dostaviti poruku
... nekom ko može pomoci.

217
00:13:59,890 --> 00:14:00,924
Ali, ja se ne usudjujem izaci odavde.

218
00:14:01,393 --> 00:14:02,718
Jesu li ti oni stvarno braca?

219
00:14:03,093 --> 00:14:04,778
Ma daj. Šta ti je?

220
00:14:05,258 --> 00:14:06,840
Dobro, zar nema neko mjesto
kamo bi mogla otici?

221
00:14:07,293 --> 00:14:08,653
Nekog, koga bi mogla nazvati?

222
00:14:09,664 --> 00:14:11,658
Moji prijatelji nisu pri telefonu.

223
00:14:13,866 --> 00:14:15,876
Mrvice kruha!

224
00:14:17,502 --> 00:14:18,602
Izvini?

225
00:14:20,392 --> 00:14:23,435
Ne vidim smisao ovog.

226
00:14:24,208 --> 00:14:25,634
Mislim, ovo nije domaci golub.

227
00:14:26,776 --> 00:14:29,565
To je samo obican
Londonski golub, znaš.

228
00:14:30,047 --> 00:14:31,571
Od onih koji seru po Lordu Nelsonu.

229
00:14:32,074 --> 00:14:33,476
Tako je.

230
00:14:34,254 --> 00:14:38,214
U redu Krrpprrr, tražiceš
markiza de Karabasa.

231
00:14:38,825 --> 00:14:40,624
Shvataš?

232
00:14:41,042 --> 00:14:42,028
Attagirl.

233
00:14:42,369 --> 00:14:44,769
E, ovo je važno,
ne smiješ...

234
00:14:45,305 --> 00:14:46,772
O, žao mi je.

235
00:14:47,774 --> 00:14:50,040
Naravno, znaš šta radiš?

236
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:05,718
Znaš,

237
00:15:05,719 --> 00:15:08,740
- ... zvucalo je gotovo kao da te
razumije? - Ma doista.

238
00:15:23,851 --> 00:15:26,813
Dakle, šta cekamo?

239
00:15:27,152 --> 00:15:28,052
Odgovor.

240
00:15:28,790 --> 00:15:30,158
Kakav odgovor?

241
00:15:34,726 --> 00:15:35,954
Slušaj,

242
00:15:36,594 --> 00:15:37,922
Kad su došli oni ljudi...

243
00:15:38,229 --> 00:15:39,597
- Krup i Vandemar
- Da

244
00:15:40,932 --> 00:15:42,266
Oni baš i nisu ljudi.

245
00:15:42,534 --> 00:15:44,202
Hriste!

246
00:15:44,737 --> 00:15:45,637
Ricarde!

247
00:15:45,740 --> 00:15:47,431
Sve je u redu, dobro je,
to je samo pacov.

248
00:15:47,653 --> 00:15:49,406
Naravno da je pacov.

249
00:15:49,641 --> 00:15:50,909
Prestravio si ga, jadnicka.

250
00:15:51,811 --> 00:15:53,179
Zdravo! Jesi li dobro?

251
00:15:53,513 --> 00:15:54,808
Izvini, on je idiot.

252
00:15:55,149 --> 00:15:56,576
Ja nisam idiot.

253
00:16:01,619 --> 00:16:03,447
To je pacov.

254
00:16:03,788 --> 00:16:05,485
Da, jeste.

255
00:16:06,190 --> 00:16:07,190
Hoceš li se izviniti?

256
00:16:07,592 --> 00:16:08,492
Šta?

257
00:16:09,403 --> 00:16:10,454
Izvini se.

258
00:16:11,497 --> 00:16:12,921
Pacovu?

259
00:16:19,698 --> 00:16:21,688
Izvini, ako sam te prepao.

260
00:16:22,583 --> 00:16:24,583
Ne, on to stvarno i misli.

261
00:16:25,583 --> 00:16:27,001
Ne govori to tek tako.

262
00:16:27,601 --> 00:16:30,383
U redu. Onda, šta imaš za mene?

263
00:16:31,539 --> 00:16:33,493
To je poruka od Karabasa.

264
00:16:34,641 --> 00:16:36,704
Samo slijedi uputstva.

265
00:16:37,916 --> 00:16:39,876
Idi na zapad od ulice Oksford,

266
00:16:40,017 --> 00:16:42,051
skreni lijevo, u ulicu Hanvej,

267
00:16:42,955 --> 00:16:43,916
lijevo u Hanvej Plejs

268
00:16:44,858 --> 00:16:46,092
onda opet desno u Orm Lejn.

269
00:16:47,129 --> 00:16:49,231
Zastani kod druge ulicne
svjetiljke na koju naidješ

270
00:16:50,102 --> 00:16:51,102
Ovo je ta.

271
00:16:51,389 --> 00:16:55,872
onda se okreni,
triput, suprotno od sunca.

272
00:16:56,244 --> 00:16:59,874
Suprotno od sunca znaci u smjeru
suprotnom od kazaljke na satu, Ricarde.

273
00:17:08,848 --> 00:17:10,812
Zdravo!

274
00:17:12,477 --> 00:17:14,255
Ima li koga?

275
00:17:15,133 --> 00:17:16,759
Ja sam Dorin prijatelj.

276
00:17:19,403 --> 00:17:21,235
Moje, vjerujem.

277
00:17:22,872 --> 00:17:24,776
De Karabas, Vama na usluzi,

278
00:17:25,006 --> 00:17:26,058
a Vi ste...

279
00:17:26,841 --> 00:17:28,203
Vi ste Ricard Mejhju,

280
00:17:28,389 --> 00:17:30,900
mladic koji je spasao
našu ranjenu Dor.

281
00:17:31,310 --> 00:17:32,210
Kako je ona sada?

282
00:17:32,410 --> 00:17:33,387
Dobro je.

283
00:17:33,679 --> 00:17:34,709
Ruka je još malo...

284
00:17:34,829 --> 00:17:36,869
Vrijeme njena oporavka
nesumnjivo ce nas sve zadiviti.

285
00:17:36,964 --> 00:17:39,729
Njena porodica ima iznimnu
moc oporavka.

286
00:17:40,544 --> 00:17:42,773
Cudo je da ih je neko uopšte i
uspio ubiti, zar ne?

287
00:17:43,062 --> 00:17:44,726
Neko je pobio Dorinu porodicu?

288
00:17:46,064 --> 00:17:46,991
Necemo stici daleko, ukoliko...

289
00:17:47,402 --> 00:17:48,302
...nastaviš...

290
00:17:48,512 --> 00:17:50,253
...ponavljati, sve što
kažem, zar ne?

291
00:17:50,424 --> 00:17:51,582
Stoga, sjedi.

292
00:17:53,337 --> 00:17:55,502
Ona zna da ja nisam jeftin.
Zašto je poslala po mene?

293
00:17:55,662 --> 00:17:56,962
U cemu je stvar?

294
00:17:57,731 --> 00:18:00,565
Rekla je da želi
da je otpratiš kuci...

295
00:18:01,100 --> 00:18:02,624
- ma gdje to bilo...
- Da

296
00:18:03,393 --> 00:18:05,231
...i želi da joj
nadeš tjelohranitelja.

297
00:18:05,636 --> 00:18:06,581
A nudi?

298
00:18:07,564 --> 00:18:09,160
Pa, ništa..

299
00:18:09,315 --> 00:18:10,287
Nudi mi,

300
00:18:10,400 --> 00:18:12,387
ništa.

301
00:18:14,135 --> 00:18:15,390
Dobro, nije rekla
ništa o novcu.

302
00:18:15,483 --> 00:18:19,268
Samo je rekla da ce
ti dugovati uslugu.

303
00:18:19,388 --> 00:18:20,563
Kakvu tacno uslugu?

304
00:18:25,205 --> 00:18:26,297
Prilicno veliku.

305
00:18:26,407 --> 00:18:28,741
Rekla je da ce ti dugovati
prilicno veliku uslugu.

306
00:18:30,709 --> 00:18:32,507
Jesi li je ostavio samu?

307
00:18:33,385 --> 00:18:34,146
Jesam...

308
00:18:34,147 --> 00:18:36,179
S Krupom i Vandemarom u blizini?

309
00:18:37,748 --> 00:18:39,472
Onda, šta cekaš? Hajde.

310
00:18:44,617 --> 00:18:46,113
Moram je odvesti do pijace.

311
00:18:46,685 --> 00:18:48,501
Sljedeca je za, mm,

312
00:18:48,955 --> 00:18:50,521
dva dana, ako se dobro prisjecam,

313
00:18:50,658 --> 00:18:51,682
što, naravno, besprekorno i cinim.

314
00:18:52,560 --> 00:18:53,519
Do tad je mogu sakriti.

315
00:18:53,629 --> 00:18:54,627
Pijaca?

316
00:18:55,164 --> 00:18:56,524
Plutajuca Pijaca.

317
00:18:56,701 --> 00:18:58,099
Ali, ne želiš da znaš o tome.

318
00:18:58,678 --> 00:19:00,611
- Zašto?
- Nema više pitanja!

319
00:19:11,718 --> 00:19:14,485
Ima neka sitnica,
koju prvo moram srediti.

320
00:19:15,057 --> 00:19:16,119
Osiguranje.

321
00:19:16,391 --> 00:19:18,392
A kada izademo na dnevnu svjetlost,
ne gledaj dolje.

322
00:19:18,559 --> 00:19:19,624
Zašto?

323
00:19:22,578 --> 00:19:24,589
Neko nije slušao, zar ne?

324
00:19:27,697 --> 00:19:29,929
Ja...ne mogu se pomaknuti.

325
00:19:30,388 --> 00:19:31,387
Naravno da možeš.

326
00:19:31,667 --> 00:19:32,963
Ili, ako ne možeš, možeš ostati
ovdje, dok ti se noge ne smrznu

327
00:19:33,006 --> 00:19:34,868
i preturiš se u poprilicno neurednu smrt.

328
00:19:37,640 --> 00:19:39,074
Kopile.

329
00:19:42,778 --> 00:19:43,709
Stari Bejli.

330
00:19:44,948 --> 00:19:46,881
Koje ocaravajuce neocekivano
iznenadjenje, da ovdje naletim na tebe.

331
00:19:47,233 --> 00:19:48,942
Ovdje nisi poželjan, de Karabas.

332
00:19:49,712 --> 00:19:50,772
Gubi se.

333
00:19:50,921 --> 00:19:52,153
Izgledaš zadivljujuce zdravo.

334
00:19:52,384 --> 00:19:55,195
I zar to nije nova jazbina
ili si vršio renoviranje? Šarmantno.

335
00:19:56,738 --> 00:19:58,497
Jesi li u redi, momcino?

336
00:19:59,717 --> 00:20:01,478
Tamo kuvam neke ptice.

337
00:20:02,020 --> 00:20:03,153
'Oceš malo? To je graktalica.

338
00:20:03,723 --> 00:20:05,321
Ne hvala

339
00:20:06,826 --> 00:20:07,923
Ne poznajem te.

340
00:20:08,597 --> 00:20:10,231
Kojoj si se baroniji zakleo na vjernost?

341
00:20:10,401 --> 00:20:11,301
Kako se zoveš?

342
00:20:11,374 --> 00:20:12,071
Zaveži.

343
00:20:12,072 --> 00:20:13,667
Ni rijeci više.

344
00:20:13,814 --> 00:20:15,939
Ljudi koji zabadaju svoje noseve
tamo gdje ih nisu željni,

345
00:20:16,007 --> 00:20:17,391
ponekad ih izgube.

346
00:20:18,575 --> 00:20:19,772
Onda.

347
00:20:21,476 --> 00:20:23,770
Duguješ mi uslugu vec
dvadeset godina, Stari Bejli.

348
00:20:24,392 --> 00:20:26,660
Veliku uslugu, i
sad se pozivam na nju.

349
00:20:27,162 --> 00:20:28,230
- Bio sam budala.
- Jesi.

350
00:20:28,352 --> 00:20:29,962
Nema budale kao stare budale.

351
00:20:31,669 --> 00:20:32,828
Znaš li šta je ovo?

352
00:20:33,773 --> 00:20:35,075
Želio bi da ne znam.

353
00:20:35,207 --> 00:20:36,201
Cuvaj mi je na sigurnom.

354
00:20:36,344 --> 00:20:37,244
Ne želim je.

355
00:20:37,580 --> 00:20:39,131
Nemaš izbora.

356
00:20:42,629 --> 00:20:45,061
U redu. Bolje da krenemo, zar ne?

357
00:20:56,527 --> 00:20:58,508
Mogu li postaviti pitanje?

358
00:20:58,644 --> 00:20:59,416
Ne.

359
00:20:59,417 --> 00:21:01,411
Ne postavljaš nikakva pitanja.

360
00:21:01,543 --> 00:21:02,421
Ne dobijaš nikakve odgovore.

361
00:21:02,422 --> 00:21:04,276
Ne skreceš sa staze.

362
00:21:04,458 --> 00:21:05,686
Cak ni ne pomišljaš
šta ti se trenutno dogadja.

363
00:21:06,408 --> 00:21:07,308
Shvataš.

364
00:21:07,467 --> 00:21:08,428
Oprosti mi.

365
00:21:08,906 --> 00:21:10,998
Znam da je ovo licno pitanje,

366
00:21:12,329 --> 00:21:14,620
ali, jesi li ti klinicki lud?

367
00:21:14,831 --> 00:21:16,596
To je poprilicno nevjerovatno, zašto?

368
00:21:17,267 --> 00:21:18,167
Pa.

369
00:21:18,470 --> 00:21:19,903
Jedan od nas mora da jeste.

370
00:21:20,604 --> 00:21:22,303
Pripazi na glavu.

371
00:21:27,608 --> 00:21:29,573
Nije u svom najboljem izdanju.

372
00:21:40,796 --> 00:21:42,257
Ricarde, uspio si.

373
00:21:42,292 --> 00:21:43,786
Pa, jesam.

374
00:21:44,533 --> 00:21:45,433
Moja Gospo.

375
00:21:45,869 --> 00:21:47,797
O, ustani, de Karabase.

376
00:21:48,439 --> 00:21:49,381
Drago mi je da si došao.

377
00:21:49,576 --> 00:21:50,476
Zadovoljstvo je moje, madam.

378
00:21:50,545 --> 00:21:52,111
Vaša je ponuda bila sasvim prihvatljiva.

379
00:21:52,315 --> 00:21:53,215
Kasnije.

380
00:21:54,572 --> 00:21:55,482
Ricarde.

381
00:21:55,726 --> 00:21:56,626
Hvala.

382
00:21:56,663 --> 00:21:57,753
Odlaziš?

383
00:21:57,931 --> 00:21:59,265
Sada cu biti sigurna.

384
00:21:59,474 --> 00:22:00,374
više-manje.

385
00:22:00,493 --> 00:22:01,393
Nadam se.

386
00:22:01,621 --> 00:22:03,583
Gdje sad ideš?

387
00:22:04,389 --> 00:22:05,951
Odlazim iz tvog života.

388
00:22:06,558 --> 00:22:08,419
I bio si divan.

389
00:22:13,332 --> 00:22:14,134
Cekaj!

390
00:22:14,135 --> 00:22:15,573
Šta ako budem morao stupiti
u kontakt s tobom?

391
00:22:16,204 --> 00:22:17,262
Neceš.

392
00:22:17,558 --> 00:22:18,458
Ikad.

393
00:22:18,490 --> 00:22:19,674
Žao mi je, u redu?

394
00:22:21,498 --> 00:22:22,340
Ne.

395
00:22:22,341 --> 00:22:23,241
Nemoj da ti je žao.

396
00:22:23,362 --> 00:22:25,758
Nema niceg za cim bi trebalo
da se žali. Bilo je...

397
00:22:27,962 --> 00:22:29,788
zabavno.

398
00:22:34,480 --> 00:22:36,143
Taksi!

399
00:22:39,223 --> 00:22:40,791
Taksi!

400
00:22:42,791 --> 00:22:44,490
Taksi!

401
00:22:46,990 --> 00:22:48,989
Ma daj!

402
00:22:53,789 --> 00:22:55,063
Izvinite što kasnim.

403
00:22:55,763 --> 00:22:57,292
Ne bi povjerovali
kako je bilo stici ovdje.

404
00:22:59,392 --> 00:23:01,098
Nocna mora.

405
00:23:02,898 --> 00:23:04,769
- Tamo.
- Kako cudno.

406
00:23:05,368 --> 00:23:06,416
Šta se dešava?

407
00:23:06,890 --> 00:23:07,707
Izvinite?

408
00:23:07,708 --> 00:23:08,560
Stol.

409
00:23:08,561 --> 00:23:10,046
Gdje odnose moj stol.

410
00:23:11,418 --> 00:23:12,528
Gari.

411
00:23:15,373 --> 00:23:16,524
Gari, šta se dešava!?

412
00:23:17,552 --> 00:23:19,324
Je li ovo nekakva šala ili tako nešto?

413
00:23:23,333 --> 00:23:25,961
Gari, ovo nije zabavno.

414
00:23:26,648 --> 00:23:29,334
Ne znam šta to svi izigravate.

415
00:23:29,421 --> 00:23:31,360
Ako sam otpušten, onda
mi recite da sam otpušten,

416
00:23:31,458 --> 00:23:33,585
ali sve ovo pretvaranje
da nisam ovdje...

417
00:23:34,032 --> 00:23:35,692
Zdravo. Ja sam Geri Perunu.

418
00:23:36,304 --> 00:23:37,204
Mogu li vam pomoci?

419
00:23:39,740 --> 00:23:40,640
Ne.

420
00:23:41,455 --> 00:23:42,601
Ne bi rekao.

421
00:23:52,406 --> 00:23:53,904
Džes...

422
00:23:54,204 --> 00:23:55,435
Džesika.

423
00:23:56,080 --> 00:23:57,265
Hvala Bogu.

424
00:23:58,424 --> 00:24:01,056
Mislim da ludim ili nešto tako.

425
00:24:01,132 --> 00:24:03,240
Vidi, stvarno mi je žao zbog one noci,

426
00:24:04,216 --> 00:24:07,368
ali ne bi vjerovala
šta mi se izdešavalo.

427
00:24:07,907 --> 00:24:09,166
Oprostite.

428
00:24:09,418 --> 00:24:11,782
Pomisliceš da sam stvarno užasna,

429
00:24:12,023 --> 00:24:13,601
Znam da smo se ranije sreli ali,

430
00:24:13,785 --> 00:24:16,259
imam doista jezivo pamcenje za lica.

431
00:24:20,443 --> 00:24:21,343
Da, gospodo Simons.

432
00:24:21,572 --> 00:24:24,025
Sutra cemo dovesti ženu da rašcisti
opremu prethodnog stanara.

433
00:24:24,220 --> 00:24:26,198
Onda možete pokupiti kljuceve
iz moje kancelarije.

434
00:24:26,906 --> 00:24:27,971
Tako je, stan 3.

435
00:24:28,532 --> 00:24:30,091
Izvinjavam se.

436
00:24:30,341 --> 00:24:31,807
Ja živim ovdje.

437
00:24:36,290 --> 00:24:39,108
Ovo se ne dešava.

438
00:24:49,698 --> 00:24:51,141
Halo?

439
00:24:51,256 --> 00:24:52,069
Gospodin Mejhju?

440
00:24:52,070 --> 00:24:53,377
Da.

441
00:24:53,717 --> 00:24:55,097
Vi me cujete.

442
00:24:55,795 --> 00:24:57,566
O havla Bogu.

443
00:24:58,077 --> 00:24:58,977
Ko je to?

444
00:24:59,130 --> 00:25:01,527
Moj partner i ja smo vas sreli u subotu.

445
00:25:01,759 --> 00:25:05,969
Vodili smo istragu koja se
se ticala stanovite mlade dame.

446
00:25:06,004 --> 00:25:07,467
Da li se sjecate?

447
00:25:07,502 --> 00:25:09,121
O, da.

448
00:25:09,156 --> 00:25:10,741
To ste vi.

449
00:25:11,109 --> 00:25:13,901
Gospodine Mejhju, rekli ste da
Dor nije bila s vama.

450
00:25:14,113 --> 00:25:15,779
Imamo razloga vjerovati da...

451
00:25:15,780 --> 00:25:19,113
...ste izbjegavali
istinu, vjerovatno više no malo.

452
00:25:19,507 --> 00:25:21,541
Pa, rekli ste da ste joj brat.

453
00:25:21,576 --> 00:25:23,575
Svi ljudi su braca, gospodine Mejhju.

454
00:25:23,610 --> 00:25:24,878
Ona nije više ovdje.

455
00:25:25,267 --> 00:25:26,162
I ne znam gdje je.

456
00:25:26,163 --> 00:25:27,027
To znamo.

457
00:25:27,028 --> 00:25:31,029
Savršeno smo svjesni obe ove cinjenice.

458
00:25:31,196 --> 00:25:33,908
I da budem ocaravajuce
iskren, gospodine Mejhju-

459
00:25:33,909 --> 00:25:36,864
a vi želite da budem iskren, zar ne?

460
00:25:36,935 --> 00:25:41,819
Da sam na vašem mjestu,
ne bih više brinuo o mladoj dami.

461
00:25:41,854 --> 00:25:43,794
Njeni su dani odbrojani,

462
00:25:43,829 --> 00:25:48,585
a broj, koji je u pitanju,
nije cak ni dvocifren.

463
00:25:48,998 --> 00:25:51,746
Slušajte, zašto me zovete?

464
00:25:51,781 --> 00:25:52,818
Gospodine Mejhju,

465
00:25:52,853 --> 00:25:57,628
znate li kakav ukus ima vaša
vlastita jetra?

466
00:25:57,663 --> 00:25:59,828
Zovem policiju.

467
00:25:59,829 --> 00:26:02,043
Ne možete mi tako prijetiti.

468
00:26:02,044 --> 00:26:04,472
Gospodine Majhju, možete zvati
koga god poželite.

469
00:26:04,473 --> 00:26:07,398
Ali ne bih volio da mislite
da vam prijetimo.

470
00:26:07,399 --> 00:26:11,329
Ni ja niti gospodin
Vandemar ne prijetimo,

471
00:26:11,330 --> 00:26:12,675
zar ne, gospodine Vandemar?

472
00:26:12,676 --> 00:26:13,576
O, ne? Onda...

473
00:26:13,577 --> 00:26:15,587
šta do davola radite?

474
00:26:15,588 --> 00:26:17,061
Mi vam dajemo obecanje.

475
00:26:17,062 --> 00:26:20,015
I znamo gdje živite.

476
00:26:28,994 --> 00:26:30,244
Znali ste.

477
00:26:35,587 --> 00:26:36,672
Kopilad.

478
00:26:42,351 --> 00:26:43,473
Znali ste da ce se ovo desiti.

479
00:26:50,537 --> 00:26:51,827
O, ne!

480
00:26:53,944 --> 00:26:55,538
Možeš li mi dati nešto sice?

481
00:26:56,088 --> 00:26:56,921
Evo.

482
00:26:56,922 --> 00:26:57,922
Zadrži.

483
00:26:57,923 --> 00:27:01,345
Tu ima oko hiljadu i po funti,

484
00:27:01,346 --> 00:27:03,518
ako možeš doci do njih.

485
00:27:03,519 --> 00:27:05,070
O, dobro.

486
00:27:05,071 --> 00:27:06,687
Vrlo dobro. Puno hvala.

487
00:27:06,688 --> 00:27:09,293
To i šezdeset penija obezbjedice
mi lijepu šolju kave.

488
00:27:09,294 --> 00:27:10,898
Ti me možeš vidjeti.

489
00:27:10,899 --> 00:27:12,223
S mojim je ocima sve u redu

490
00:27:12,224 --> 00:27:14,781
Slušaj, jesi li ikad cuo za
mjesto zvano 'Plutajuca pijaca'?

491
00:27:15,449 --> 00:27:16,504
Moram stici tamo.

492
00:27:17,269 --> 00:27:18,786
Tamo je djevojka zvana Dor.

493
00:27:18,787 --> 00:27:19,898
Vidi,

494
00:27:21,685 --> 00:27:22,756
Stvarno mi je potrebna pomoc.

495
00:27:24,304 --> 00:27:25,359
Molim te?

496
00:27:27,450 --> 00:27:29,735
Dobro, izvini što sam te gnjavio.

497
00:27:29,736 --> 00:27:30,838
Hej,

498
00:27:33,762 --> 00:27:34,956
dolje,

499
00:27:35,416 --> 00:27:36,316
Brzo.

500
00:27:40,448 --> 00:27:42,662
I, zašto me ti možeš vidjeti...

501
00:27:42,663 --> 00:27:44,083
...kada niko drugi ne može.

502
00:27:44,084 --> 00:27:45,772
Nije da te ne mogu vidjeti.

503
00:27:45,773 --> 00:27:46,881
Oni te vide...

504
00:27:46,882 --> 00:27:47,961
...ali te ne gledaju.

505
00:27:48,237 --> 00:27:49,029
Ne primjecuju te

506
00:27:49,030 --> 00:27:50,282
i dok zadješ za ugao

507
00:27:50,373 --> 00:27:51,610
vec su te zaboravili.

508
00:27:52,110 --> 00:27:53,367
Isto se i meni dogodilo.

509
00:27:53,976 --> 00:27:55,132
Gdje me vodiš.

510
00:27:55,133 --> 00:27:55,760
Dolje.

511
00:27:55,761 --> 00:27:58,281
Neke ljude koje bi, mislim, morao vidjeti.

512
00:28:11,195 --> 00:28:12,325
Šta?

513
00:28:12,439 --> 00:28:15,061
Šta je to? Šta je ovo?

514
00:28:17,135 --> 00:28:19,231
Koga si nam to doveo, Ilijastere?

515
00:28:19,832 --> 00:28:21,708
Govori.

516
00:28:21,709 --> 00:28:23,215
GOVORI!

517
00:28:23,216 --> 00:28:24,488
On je iz Gornjeg svijeta.

518
00:28:24,960 --> 00:28:27,122
Raspituje se o Plutajucoj pijaci.

519
00:28:27,123 --> 00:28:28,487
...i o Dor.

520
00:28:28,488 --> 00:28:29,912
Doveo sam ga Vama
Gospodaru pacovski glasnik.

521
00:28:29,913 --> 00:28:31,487
Smatrao sam da bi Vi znali šta s njim.

522
00:28:31,488 --> 00:28:32,438
O da.

523
00:28:33,308 --> 00:28:34,208
Da.

524
00:28:35,134 --> 00:28:38,359
Znam tacno šta uraditi s njim.

